definitions.definition: A village and civil parish (served by Gamston with West Drayton and Eaton Parish Council) in Bassetlaw district, Nottinghamshire , England ( OS grid ref SK7176 ) .
A suburban village and civil parish (served by Holme Pierrepont and Gamston Parish Council) in Rushcliffe borough , Nottinghamshire ( OS grid ref SK6037 ) .
